Slide 11 â€“ On-Prem Challenges & Fixes

Issue	Reason	Fix
SSL / Certificate trust error	On-prem Jira cert not trusted	Import Jira cert into Jenkins JVM truststore
Jenkins cannot trigger Jira	Firewall restrictions	Whitelist ports 443/8080
Jira REST API blocked	Permissions issue	Add API token + required roles
Wrong Issue Key	Devs forget to add key	Validate in pipeline


